  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseInsect2">
    <defName>AA_BlackSpelopede</defName>
    <label>black spelopede</label>
    <description>A medium-sized bioengineered insectoid the size of a sheep that is part of the Black Hive, an artifical ecosystem of insectoids designed to fight mechanoid invasions. The Black Hive was designed to be much more aggressive than usual, and several new species were created and added to the Hive to increase its lethality. The spelopede is the middle caste of a hive, taking care of most work tasks as well as fighting with its digging claws. It's dangerous in combat, but slow on open ground.</description>
